WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.389 --> 00:00:01.314
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.314 --> 00:00:03.549
I'm excited to be with y'all today.

00:00:03.811 --> 00:00:06.835
I have a pretty strong word from the Lord.

00:00:07.875 --> 00:00:13.260
I just got off social media completely; this word was so strong.

00:00:13.260 --> 00:00:18.639
I've had two very strong words in the last week from the Lord.

00:00:18.639 --> 00:00:32.226
I had one visitation from the Father, and the presence of the Lord filled my house so strongly—I can honestly tell you I've never felt the presence of the Lord like that before.

00:00:32.719 --> 00:00:41.945
It shook me and gave me a renewed fear in Him of how close we are to Jesus coming.

00:00:43.220 --> 00:00:50.887
I'm going to start off with this: He told me, 'It's time to get serious.

00:00:51.620 --> 00:00:58.309
You're not serious enough; you're not pushing and pursuing enough for what's coming.

00:00:58.309 --> 00:01:01.760
' He said there's a shifting taking place.

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:11.826
It all started while I was praying over Israel, and He was speaking to me about the meeting that President Biden had with Benjamin Netanyahu yesterday.

00:01:12.320 --> 00:01:19.626
He said there's going to be an acceleration of times and an acceleration of things now.

00:01:20.360 --> 00:01:41.560
You'll see an acceleration with war, with financial stuff, and with the signs of the heavens—outer space stuff.

00:01:41.560 --> 00:02:00.026
There's going to be acceleration with the weather and our atmosphere.

00:02:01.579 --> 00:02:23.965
He said these are times like you've never seen before; the Earth has never experienced what it's about to experience in the coming days.

00:02:31.690 --> 00:02:32.100
It is an acceleration into unprecedented times.

00:02:32.100 --> 00:02:45.509
We have never in history experienced what we're about to experience.

00:02:45.509 --> 00:02:57.027
There was so much pressure in the Spirit when He said this.

00:02:59.586 --> 00:03:13.420
He warned me about what's coming and said, 'The body of Christ is not awake.

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:22.263
The people in the prophetic realm are not awake.

00:03:22.263 --> 00:03:44.660
' He was talking about coming up higher and said, 'The level you're operating in right now is a very shallow level.

00:03:44.660 --> 00:03:58.299
It's time to come up higher with Me; it's time to separate yourself even more than you already have.

00:03:58.299 --> 00:04:36.919
' He said, 'Brandon, there's a level of prophetic that the world has never experienced before, and you must separate yourself to hear Me closely for what is coming to warn the people.

00:04:36.919 --> 00:04:50.253
' He said many of His people are not hearing or listening.

00:04:50.253 --> 00:05:20.940
We are in very serious times, for the coming of His Son is at hand, yet people are asleep.

00:05:20.940 --> 00:05:30.980
Some feel they are awake, but they're still not.

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:57.063
He was even correcting me, saying I was spending way too much time talking to people on Facebook and answering questions.

00:05:57.063 --> 00:06:24.420
He said that's not what I'm here to do; I am to seek Him, stay at His feet, and deliver the word He has for the people.

00:06:24.420 --> 00:06:42.993
It was a rebuke, so I erased Facebook and all the things that were a distraction.

00:06:45.445 --> 00:06:58.173
I want to go higher; I don't want to be in the shallow water.

00:06:58.173 --> 00:07:29.450
I want to be over my head, all the way to the bottom, saturated and controlled by the Holy Ghost for these last days.

00:07:29.450 --> 00:07:47.893
He had me praying for the tunnels in Israel for the ground invasion, and I saw things plotted against the soldiers.

00:07:55.960 --> 00:08:09.240
The Lord warned me to pray against booby traps and explosives rigged to harm people, including the hostages.

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:39.120
We need to intercede for those people, sending angels to help because the enemy is ruthless, without a conscience, like barbarians.

00:08:44.177 --> 00:09:00.180
I won't go into a lot regarding the tie between Israel and the United States; it's just not smart.

00:09:08.040 --> 00:09:34.380
This is the second part: after He warned me about the acceleration of war, times, finances, and the shift to cryptocurrencies, He warned me about 2024 and what's coming.

00:09:37.590 --> 00:09:58.720
In my prayer time, when the glory manifested so strongly, He warned me again about coming up higher.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:42.480
It's been six days since my visitation, and He said, 'It's time to come up higher in the prophetic realm and in walking with Me, for I long for you to abide in the fire.

00:10:42.480 --> 00:11:13.560
' Suddenly, I saw the heavens split above me—a massive break in the atmosphere—and I saw the Lord seated on His throne, the great God Jehovah.

00:11:13.560 --> 00:11:30.080
I saw this massive light coming out and Him seated on His throne.

00:11:46.392 --> 00:11:46.748
I want you all to grasp this: Heaven is invading Earth now.

00:11:46.748 --> 00:11:58.140
It's an invasion of Heaven on Earth like we've never seen.

00:12:05.650 --> 00:12:16.497
I saw a liquid lava flowing out of the throne of God that looked like liquid honey.

00:12:20.395 --> 00:12:43.109
It was moving slowly but beautifully, with sparkles of gold dust inside, oozing out onto the Earth.

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:55.320
It was tiered as I was looking up in the throne room.

00:12:55.320 --> 00:13:06.589
Then the Lord allowed me to see inside of Him.

00:13:12.205 --> 00:13:18.986
A lot of you will probably squawk about this, but I really don't care.

00:13:18.986 --> 00:13:31.943
God is light, and in Him there is no darkness at all.

00:13:31.943 --> 00:14:13.470
He allowed me to see the light as His skin, and then he allowed my spiritual eyes to see inside of the Father, great El Elyon, the most high God.

00:14:22.614 --> 00:14:28.900
I say this with fear and reverence: the light is like His skin.

00:14:28.900 --> 00:14:39.820
Inside Him, He was endless—His own dimension.

00:14:57.680 --> 00:15:00.543
It looked like a different kind of light, with unique stars shining all inside of Him.

00:15:10.088 --> 00:15:10.351
It moved like it was alive, transparent and spirit.

00:15:12.600 --> 00:15:20.609
It had a shape and was taking form, though it's hard to explain.

00:15:22.853 --> 00:15:37.470
I saw the silhouette of His face from afar, with a crown on His head.

00:15:37.470 --> 00:15:48.169
Inside His head, I could see three beautiful blue sapphires—huge ones.

00:15:54.693 --> 00:15:59.934
All around was a beautiful light like blue fire, making the sapphires glow.

00:15:59.934 --> 00:16:26.017
Around His face, I could only see His chin and the back of His head; everything else was fire radiating a captivating blue light.

00:16:26.017 --> 00:16:41.591
I was fixed on it; I felt like I was melting like wax in my home.

00:16:41.591 --> 00:16:56.382
It was the most holy moment, seeing a glimpse of the silhouette of the Father.

00:16:56.382 --> 00:17:05.400
Then He said, 'Focus and see this wall.

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:23.360
' Upon the wall was ancient text, eons of time, with angelic writing engraved into stone with fire.

00:17:23.360 --> 00:17:37.070
This was writing on a granite rock with triangles, circles, waves, and squares.

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:50.810
He told me it was an ancient text etched in for millions of years.

00:17:58.244 --> 00:18:15.039
I still don't have the full revelation of why He showed me this, but it was being downloaded like a fire hydrant.

00:18:17.035 --> 00:18:29.966
He said, 'My prophetic people are thinking too carnal; it's time to come up another level.

00:18:29.966 --> 00:18:41.540
' He even told me my thinking was too shallow.

00:18:41.540 --> 00:19:06.299
He asked, 'Do you know the difference between a flash in the pan and someone who stands the test of time?

00:19:06.299 --> 00:19:28.546
' He told me not to be a flash in the pan but a pillar who teaches the word.

00:19:36.974 --> 00:20:03.914
He brought up brother Kenneth Hagin, saying brother Hagin didn't just give a word of the day; he taught the people how to live by faith and stand on the covenant.

00:20:03.914 --> 00:20:18.823
To stand the test of time, you must teach the word.

00:20:18.823 --> 00:20:37.005
Too many prophetic people are just a flash in the pan and will burn out.

00:20:37.005 --> 00:20:49.440
It's about getting in the word and teaching the people how to pray.

00:20:53.584 --> 00:21:06.800
He said, 'When you seek Me daily and come out of carnal thinking, I will give you those words.

00:21:06.800 --> 00:21:19.740
' We are in a season of great birthing pains, more than ever before.

00:21:34.600 --> 00:21:34.760
What we've experienced is nothing compared to what is about to happen.

00:21:34.760 --> 00:21:51.363
He said this as a warning to sit at His feet and make Him priority number one.

00:21:51.363 --> 00:22:05.260
He was showing me levels of the prophetic: ankle-deep, waist-deep, knee-deep, and then over the head.

00:22:05.260 --> 00:22:25.852
He said, 'Brandon, there's so much more than what you're seeing on YouTube; you're just scratching the surface.

00:22:25.852 --> 00:22:51.680
' If you abide in Him, sit at His table, and take your seat in heavenly places above principalities and powers, you walk in dominion.

00:22:51.680 --> 00:23:00.464
It's like breathing: inhale the Father, exhale.

00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:19.849
He said, 'Sit at My throne, and that's when you give the word to the people.

00:23:19.849 --> 00:23:43.306
' Going back to the three sapphires, I believe they represented the Father, the Son, and the Holy Ghost—all three are one inside of Him.

00:23:43.306 --> 00:23:55.183
My words in the English vocabulary don't do it justice.

00:24:04.693 --> 00:24:16.169
It was a lot of correction for me to separate myself from comments and worrying about what people think.

00:24:16.169 --> 00:24:28.149
He's showing me it's about separation and flowing in the Holy Spirit.

00:24:39.559 --> 00:24:40.024
Then He showed me Israel.

00:24:40.024 --> 00:24:54.889
I saw darkness all around it like a wall, but light came down from Heaven.

00:24:54.889 --> 00:25:12.680
I was above the Earth looking down, seeing a wall of protection in the spirit realm over Israel.

00:25:18.733 --> 00:25:19.227
He was honoring His covenant.

00:25:19.720 --> 00:25:53.520
He told me to pay attention to the Mediterranean; while there was no darkness on the sea, there were walls of demonic activity on the borders from Egypt all around.

00:25:58.929 --> 00:26:02.635
I interceded against sneak attacks from the sea.

00:26:02.635 --> 00:26:15.930
Then He took me over America, and I saw the southern border with people coming across.

00:26:15.930 --> 00:26:33.004
America looked gray, with a gray sludge over it, but there was still light shining; it was not total darkness.

00:26:33.856 --> 00:26:45.404
I asked if there would be an attack on Friday the 13th.

00:26:45.404 --> 00:26:57.760
He laughed and said, 'Brandon, they're never going to announce when that's going to happen.

00:26:57.760 --> 00:27:14.640
' He said it's a surprise attack, like Israel's, so you must pray against hidden things so you aren't blindsided.

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:26.105
Nothing happened on those days, but He was telling me to stay on my guard.

00:27:26.105 --> 00:27:28.624
I'll end there.

00:27:28.624 --> 00:27:35.086
This bell is our new notification signal, so please subscribe if this video blessed you.

00:27:35.086 --> 00:27:48.906
I won't share more of the vision right now as I don't feel it's wisdom.

00:27:48.906 --> 00:28:00.544
Let's pray we are always in the right place at the right time.

00:28:10.653 --> 00:28:10.867
The eclipse was very significant—a sign in the heavens.

00:28:10.867 --> 00:28:26.920
Things are fixing to get amazing; the light will get lighter and the dark darker.

00:28:26.920 --> 00:28:30.467
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:28:30.467 --> 00:28:49.939
People argue about 'once saved, always saved,' but I'm telling you, you need to listen to those walking with Jesus.

00:28:55.219 --> 00:28:57.319
You can backslide, so get your heart right.

00:28:57.319 --> 00:29:09.164
I'm not here to condemn you, but to lift you up.

00:29:09.164 --> 00:29:14.987
Don't compromise or live in sin.

00:29:14.987 --> 00:29:34.893
You won't go to hell for smoking a cigarette, but those who practice sin without repentance are on the 'Highway to Hell.

00:29:34.893 --> 00:29:49.679
' We should be like the virgins keeping our lamps full, having communion with Him daily.

00:29:49.679 --> 00:29:55.653
The wages of sin is death.

00:29:58.990 --> 00:30:03.271
Jesus said, 'Go and sin no more, lest a worse thing come upon you.

00:30:03.271 --> 00:30:11.554
' We have to live separate lives for Him.

00:30:16.520 --> 00:30:21.279
I walk with Jesus, and if you listen, I'll help you.

00:30:21.279 --> 00:30:30.164
We're at a point of separation; it's not a game anymore.

00:30:30.519 --> 00:30:37.832
Choose the Lord today with all your heart.

00:30:37.832 --> 00:30:51.839
Father, we thank You that You are a loving God, full of mercy.

00:31:02.559 --> 00:31:04.531
Your mercies are new every morning.

00:31:10.820 --> 00:31:15.860
You healed our diseases and took our infirmities.

00:31:34.428 --> 00:31:37.840
No weapon formed against us shall prosper.

00:31:37.840 --> 00:31:45.124
We take authority over the devil in the name of Jesus and tell him to cease and desist.

00:31:47.532 --> 00:31:52.209
We take authority over demonic spirits coming against our children.

00:31:52.209 --> 00:32:07.484
We call in wayward children and unsaved loved ones, and we call laborers across their path.

00:32:07.484 --> 00:32:28.804
I pray for the salvation of that man's wife; soften her heart and give her an experience with You in the midnight hour.

00:32:31.080 --> 00:32:47.674
For those believing for their husbands, let the glory of God shake them in their sleep.

00:32:55.027 --> 00:33:02.159
Give them a dream of You, or even of hell, to lead them to Jesus.

00:33:15.296 --> 00:33:17.640
Let the natural become supernatural.

00:33:17.640 --> 00:33:35.617
We plead the blood of Jesus over our loved ones and call for the restoration of marriages and households.

00:33:36.970 --> 00:33:45.424
We are the salt and light of this earth.

00:33:54.778 --> 00:33:59.639
We lay hands on the sick, cast out devils, and raise the dead.

00:34:02.164 --> 00:34:21.136
We pray for revelation knowledge and that the eyes of our understanding be enlightened to know You intimately.

00:34:24.270 --> 00:34:38.248
We are joint heirs with Jesus Christ, redeemed from the curse of the law.

00:34:38.248 --> 00:34:45.987
By Your stripes, we are healed.

00:34:59.542 --> 00:34:59.908
You made a display of triumph over the devil and gave us authority.

00:35:02.670 --> 00:35:07.349
We take authority over addictions, perversions, and drugs.

00:35:07.349 --> 00:35:12.947
We bind depression, anxiety, and fear.

00:35:27.666 --> 00:35:27.893
We call for hormone balance over serotonin, cortisol, and adrenals.

00:35:31.034 --> 00:35:39.030
I thank You for babies and restored marriages.

00:35:39.030 --> 00:35:51.060
I thank You for spiritual babies growing through this channel.

00:35:51.060 --> 00:36:03.503
They will rise up, take their authority, and steamroll the devil—a toothless lion.

00:36:03.503 --> 00:36:20.120
We are not afraid; we raise the sword of the Spirit.

00:36:20.120 --> 00:36:36.053
We renew our minds and go from the ankle-deep water to the deeps.

00:36:36.053 --> 00:36:43.840
We give You praise in Jesus' name, amen.

00:36:43.840 --> 00:36:54.909
I'm not on Facebook anymore; it's time to go deeper in the word.

00:36:54.909 --> 00:37:06.520
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:37:06.520 --> 00:37:08.720
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:37:08.720 --> 00:37:12.150
Have a blessed day.

00:37:12.150 --> 00:37:13.010
Bye-bye.
